text: Eleni Giannou (born 16 September 1993) is a Cypriot footballer who plays as a midfielder for First Division club Pyrgos Limassol FC and the Cyprus women's national team. ==Career== Giannou has been capped for the Cyprus national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Cypriot women's footballers Category:Cyprus women's international footballers Category:Apollon Ladies F.C. players Category:PAOK FC (women) players Category:Cypriot expatriate footballers Category:Cypriot expatriate sportspeople in Greece Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Greece
